msgstr ""

#: 10_15P01
msgid "I'm ready to leave now, Horst."
msgstr ""

#: 10_15P02
msgid "Ah, better make it cash then."
msgstr ""

#: 10_16N01
msgid "They are good here, Ripley."
msgstr ""

#: 10_16P01
msgid "Change my mind."
msgstr ""

#: 11_01N01
msgid "It is the damp. Almost a swamp is here."
msgstr ""

#: 11_01N02
msgid "You will have noticed unusual features?"
msgstr ""

#: 11_01N04
msgid "Ja, mein Herr."
msgstr ""

#: 11_01N05
msgid "It is a long story, mein Herr."
msgstr ""

#: 11_01N06
msgid "Yeah, he did. I carry it."
msgstr ""

#: 11_01N07
msgid "Perhaps I'll talk to you later, if I may."
msgstr ""

#: 11_01P01
msgid "What a melancholy aspect this place presents."
msgstr ""

#: 11_01P02
msgid "An impressive tomb the old baron rests in."
msgstr ""

