#: 14_08P02
msgid "That's it?"
msgstr ""

#: 14_09N01
msgid "And your business, Mein Herr, is of no interest to me."
msgstr ""

#: 14_09P01
msgid "My dear fellow, your business is your own, and of no interest to me."
msgstr ""

#: 14_14N01
msgid "It was a high stakes poker game many years ago at the baron's club. It is said the money on the table for that single hand would rival the treasury of several smaller nations. The old baron drew the ace of spades to complete a royal flush and win the hand."
msgstr ""

#: 14_14N02
msgid "Just so."
