#: 16_01N02
msgid "Muy bien, señor Ripley."
msgstr ""

#: 16_01N03
msgid "How much inti will you like, senor?"
msgstr ""

#: 16_01N08
msgid "Vaya con Dios, senor."
msgstr ""

#: 16_01P01
msgid "I'd like to book passage."
msgstr ""

#: 16_01P02
msgid "I'd like to send a parcel to New York."
msgstr ""

#: 16_01P03
msgid "I'd like to buy some of your local currency."
msgstr ""

#: 16_01P04
msgid "Sooo, we're back, we're like, I'm in the shit, this little broom again, but we're sike, it's the sii-"
